Interface KubernetesObject

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface KubernetesObject
Defines methods for Kubernetes resource wrappers that retrieve application specifications.

    • getApplicationSpecs

      List<ApplicationSpec> getApplicationSpecs(io.fabric8.kubernetes.client.KubernetesClient client, boolean anyNamespace, List<String> matchNames)
      Retrieves the list of ApplicationSpec from the Kubernetes cluster.
      Parameters:
      client - Kubernetes client instance
      anyNamespace - if true, search across all namespaces; otherwise use matchNames
      matchNames - list of namespaces to filter on, used only if anyNamespace is false
      Returns:
      list of ApplicationSpec found
